                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2452-18371023 t18371023-2452-punishment-224"></join>Confined Six Months; One Month Solitary</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant,</hi>
